headline: Dialpad Recognized in 2025 Gartner® Magic Quadrant™ for Contact Center as a Service
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, September 09, 2025--Dialpad, Inc., the leading AI-powered communications and agentic platform, today announced it has received an Honorable Mention in the 2025 Gartner® Magic Quadrant™ for Contact Center as a Service (CCaaS). This marks the ﬁrst year Gartner has introduced an Honorable Mention category within the CCaaS Magic Quadrant, and Dialpad is proud to be included.
